<td valign="top" align="left" style="border-left: solid 5px #f0f0f0;;padding:0px 5px 0px 15px;">




<strong>Studio Album, released in 1975</strong><br><br>

<strong>Songs / Tracks Listing</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">1. Comin' Home (3:52)<br>2. Lady Luck (2:45)<br>3. Gettin' Tighter (3:36)<br>4. Dealer (3:49)<br>5. I Need Love (4:22)<br>6. Drifter (4:01)<br>7. Love Child (3:05)<br>8. Medley (6:07) :<br>- a) This Time Around<br>- b) Owed to 'G'<br>9. You Keep On Moving (5:18)<br><br>Total Time 36:55</p>

<strong>Line-up / Musicians</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">- David Coverdale / lead vocals (1,2,4-7,9)<br>- Tommy Bolin / lead guitar, lead (4) & backing (1) vocals, bass (1)<br>- Jon Lord / keyboards (piano, synth)<br>- Glenn Hughes / bass, lead (3,8,9) & backing vocals<br>- Ian Paice / drums</p>

<strong>Releases information</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">
